The paper addresses the problem of novel view synthesis, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach proposed involves training a convolutional neural network (CNN), which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of appearance flows, which are related to optical flow and image registration, topics in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
